tr.th: Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us

tr.td: All parameters are within normal limits except for elevated HbA1c (6.4%), indicating impaired glucose metabolism or possible diabetes mellitus. Recommend clinical evaluation for diabetes and consideration of lifestyle or therapeutic interventions. Other renal and electrolyte parameters are unremarkable.
